@startuml WebFlux Controller Registration State Machine
[*] --> ConfigurationLoaded : Server context starts

ConfigurationLoaded --> ScanningRoutes : DynamicControllerRegister init()
ScanningRoutes --> MappingRoutes : Discover dynamic paths from CrudEngine

MappingRoutes --> RoutesBound : RouterFunctions.route() matches resources
RoutesBound --> ServerListening : Netty / Tomcat starts

state ServerListening {
  [*] --> RequestReceived
  RequestReceived --> ResolvingContext : Extract tenant/user from JWT context
  ResolvingContext --> ProcessingHandler : Dispatch to handler method
  ProcessingHandler --> DispatchingResponse : Map returned Mono/Flux to ServerResponse
  DispatchingResponse --> RequestReceived : Completed
}

ServerListening --> [*] : Server shutdown
@enduml
